metadata.name: Paris for Two
metadata.description:
What is more satisfying than breathing in a romantic balcony atmosphere with the Eiffel tower view?
The city of love is not just a random nickname, Paris evokes emotions and renovates the souls. With having a great respect to the Jojo Moyes, Paris is created for two!
Software: Revit, 3dmax, Lumion
Frame: 201
Length: 7s
